      "text_excerpt": "RACELOGIC - Experts in positioning, data\nlogging and video\nSkip to main content\nPrivacy & Cookies\nDistributor area\nSuppliers\nSupport Centre\nExperts in positioning, data\nlogging and video\nVehicle Testing\nVBOX is internationally recognised as a quality standard in speed measurement, braking distance measurement, vehicle dynamics and tyre testing.\nvboxautomotive.co.uk\nMotorsport\nDesigned for racing drivers, track day enthusiasts, and teams, the VBOX Motorsport range includes graphically enhanced\nvideo data loggers, lap timers and performance meters\n– all built to help you go faster.\nvboxmotorsport.co.uk\nGNSS Simulation\nCompact, battery powered, and versatile, LabSat GNSS simulators allow you to\nrecord live-sky satellite signals\n, synchronised with CAN and digital inputs, for\nreplay in the lab\nlabsat.co.uk\nCamera Tracking\nAirPixel delivers cutting-edge\ncamera tracking\nfor AR in broadcast, virtual production, and live events. Its ultra-precise position and orientation data, combined with integrated FIZ and genlock, make it ideal for both\nstudio and wide-area environments.\nairpixel.com\nGPS Underground\nTunnelSat is an advanced tunnel GPS system that extends reliable\nsatellite navigation underground\n, delivering accurate, real-time positioning signals.\ntunnelsat.com\nPositioning\nWe provide advanced 3D positioning and measurement systems for indoor and GPS denied environments, delivering an accuracy of ±2 cm.\nvboxpositioning.com\nMining\nOur cost-effective GPS solutions help mining companies around the world to measure precise vehicle movements and reduce tyre, fuel and maintenance costs for mining vehicles.\nvboxmining.com\nOver 30 years of innovation\nRACELOGIC design and manufacture electronic systems to measure, record, display, analyse and simulate data from moving vehicles.\nRACELOGIC thrives on technical innovation and has grown steadily since its formation in 1992, employing more than 100 people across three locations.\nWe have a global customer-base with sales to over 100 countries made via our distributor network which is based in more than 50 countries.\nWith a heritage originating in automotive and motorsport, our innovations have taken us into new sectors including aerospace, rail, marine, defence and security, health, agriculture, and most recently, film and gaming.\nRead more\nRACELOGIC UK\nin Buckingham, UK\nRACELOGIC Germany\nin Wetzlar, Hesse\nRACELOGIC France\nin Saint-Quentin-Fallavier\nRACELOGIC USA\nin Novi, Michigan\nJoin the team\nHead of Engineering (UK)\nYou will have direct responsibility for the day-to-day operational leadership of four core engineering departments: Hardware Design, Firmware, Software, and Testing.\nReporting to the Chief Technology Officer, the role encompasses line management of four department managers, end-to-end ownership of engineering delivery, and cross-functional coordination across all Racelogic brands.\nSee full job description\nProduction Technician (UK)\nWe are seeking a Production Technician to support the build, diagnosi"
